WEBVTT

00:00:06.570 --> 00:00:10.550
ROZMOWA Z PANEM HENRYKIEM ROBAKIEM

00:00:10.550 --> 00:00:11.673
PAN HENRYK

00:00:11.673 --> 00:00:15.570
ROBAK MÓWI W JIDYSZ, KASETA DRUGA.

00:00:17.360 --> 00:00:20.330
un nokh der milkhome, ikh hob gearbet in gevise

00:00:20.330 --> 00:00:23.260
yidish- poylishe institutsyes,

00:00:24.880 --> 00:00:27.240
in melukhe-amt,

00:00:28.680 --> 00:00:34.440
biz zibn un zekhtsik, akht un zekhtsikstn yor,

00:00:34.600 --> 00:00:40.630
demols ven s'iz geshen di mageyfe gegn yidn

00:00:40.630 --> 00:00:41.936
in Poyln,

00:00:42.313 --> 00:00:44.299
bin ikh bafrayt gevorn

00:00:44.777 --> 00:00:48.300
un formel fun demolt on bin ikh a rentsist,

00:00:49.190 --> 00:00:51.340
nor gezelshaftlekh

00:00:51.459 --> 00:00:53.175
arbet ikh vayter

00:00:53.383 --> 00:00:55.335
un bin vayter tetik.

00:00:56.220 --> 00:00:58.223
dos ken ikh nor tsugebn

00:00:58.223 --> 00:00:59.232
un zogn.

00:01:01.449 --> 00:01:02.796
un s'iz shver

00:01:02.796 --> 00:01:04.296
tsu dertseyln

00:01:04.780 --> 00:01:10.314
dos zeks un zibetsik-, zeks un zekhtsikstn, zibn un zekhtsikstn un akht un zekhtsikstn yor,

00:01:10.314 --> 00:01:11.990
vos s'iz geshen in Poyln.

00:01:14.440 --> 00:01:17.920
mit dem hob ikh opgehakt. ikh vil iber hoypt

00:01:17.990 --> 00:01:19.610
vegn di yorn

00:01:19.610 --> 00:01:21.103
nisht redn.

00:01:22.210 --> 00:01:24.309
far mir iz dos gevezn

00:01:25.142 --> 00:01:30.580
a farsholtener veg,

00:01:31.920 --> 00:01:33.950
un derfar vil ikh nisht dermonen.

00:01:34.480 --> 00:01:36.330
tsveytns,

00:01:37.010 --> 00:01:39.280
di shpeterdike yorn,

00:01:39.610 --> 00:01:42.080
vifl mol ikh hob zikh fartrakht,

00:01:42.500 --> 00:01:43.830
vos zits ikh

00:01:43.830 --> 00:01:45.200
nokh in Poyln?

00:01:46.235 --> 00:01:51.800
ober dos iz shoyn geven farbundn mit der mishpokhe,

00:01:52.130 --> 00:01:53.807
s'iz shoyn nisht geven

00:01:54.100 --> 00:01:55.714
di meglekhkeyt,

00:01:56.220 --> 00:01:58.060
azoy vi me zogt, aroysforn.

00:01:58.160 --> 00:02:00.260
un mayn kheyshek iz gevezn

00:02:00.260 --> 00:02:01.755
farlozn Poyln,

00:02:02.283 --> 00:02:05.062
vayl do iz umgekumen mayn gantse mishpokhe,

00:02:05.680 --> 00:02:08.860
dernokhn hob ikh zikh getrofn

00:02:08.920 --> 00:02:10.193
mit dem,

00:02:10.282 --> 00:02:11.998
azoy vi me ge- zogt,

00:02:12.155 --> 00:02:13.668
mit dem virklekhn

00:02:13.758 --> 00:02:15.761
antisemitizm in Poyln.

00:02:16.796 --> 00:02:20.233
ober dos iz gevezn,

00:02:20.610 --> 00:02:22.640
s'iz arayn in der geshikhte.

00:02:23.840 --> 00:02:27.620
vos ken ikh nor tsugebn tsu dem alem?

00:02:28.520 --> 00:02:30.520
ikh ken nor tsugebn,

00:02:31.080 --> 00:02:32.821
ikh hob a mishpokhe,

00:02:34.920 --> 00:02:36.900
di kinder mayne,

00:02:36.900 --> 00:02:38.260
di froy,

00:02:39.920 --> 00:02:42.204
zenen nisht farbundn,

00:02:42.699 --> 00:02:44.094
azoy vi me zogt,

00:02:45.770 --> 00:02:47.958
fizish, mitn yidntum.

00:02:48.352 --> 00:02:52.800
ober mora- moralish mitn yi- mitn yidntum zenen zey farbundn.

00:02:55.290 --> 00:02:56.320
bay mir

00:02:56.320 --> 00:02:59.520
iz nishto in shtub, keyn mol nisht geven, keyn tseylem,

00:02:59.520 --> 00:03:01.210
nisht bay di kinder.

00:03:01.667 --> 00:03:03.120
bay mir in shtub,

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:06.099
akhuts dem vos s'iz do yidishe tsaytungen, yidishe bikher,

00:03:06.341 --> 00:03:09.310
iz oykh do a yidishe menoyre shteyt.

00:03:10.750 --> 00:03:13.050
mir hobn keyn shum shaykhes nisht

00:03:13.140 --> 00:03:16.443
mit keyn shum religye, nisht mit der katoylisher,

00:03:16.787 --> 00:03:17.996
un nisht mit dem,

00:03:18.474 --> 00:03:21.506
azoy vi me zogt, mit dem, mitn religyezn JUDAIZM.

00:03:22.743 --> 00:03:26.636
mir zenen forgeshritene mentshn,

00:03:26.692 --> 00:03:29.710
a forgeshritene mishpokhe.

00:03:32.784 --> 00:03:35.208
un vos, un vos makhn di kinder?

00:03:35.822 --> 00:03:37.031
di kinder.

00:03:37.442 --> 00:03:38.921
eyn tokhter

00:03:40.715 --> 00:03:42.346
hot geendikt

00:03:42.530 --> 00:03:44.034
di hoykh-shule.

00:03:44.230 --> 00:03:45.970
zi iz a fizikerin.

00:03:47.837 --> 00:03:49.013
der zun

00:03:49.946 --> 00:03:51.695
hot geendikt

00:03:51.836 --> 00:03:53.400
dem tekhnikum

00:03:53.750 --> 00:03:54.919
als shloser.

00:03:55.820 --> 00:03:57.710
di yingere tokhter

00:03:58.430 --> 00:04:00.720
hot geendikt di hoykh-shule

00:04:02.653 --> 00:04:03.947
A.W.F.

00:04:04.430 --> 00:04:05.752
dos heyst,

00:04:05.970 --> 00:04:07.710
di akademye

00:04:08.720 --> 00:04:11.754
fun fizishe shuln.

00:04:11.799 --> 00:04:14.629
AKADEMIA WYCHOWANIA FIZYCZNEGO.

00:04:13.233 --> 00:04:14.189
HIGHER

00:04:14.330 --> 00:04:19.471
HIGHERe HIGHERe fizi- fizikalishe shule (oder azoy vos), fizishe shule (oder azoy vos).

00:04:19.697 --> 00:04:20.822
un dos,

00:04:21.367 --> 00:04:25.141
nu, un di kinder in di rikhtung arbetn.

00:04:26.250 --> 00:04:27.820
a bisl (inem) lebn,

00:04:27.820 --> 00:04:29.473
dos lebn geyt beser,

00:04:29.473 --> 00:04:31.064
a bisl erger,

00:04:31.357 --> 00:04:34.370
azoy vi s'zet oys di lage in Poyln.

00:04:35.020 --> 00:04:35.992
nu, yo.

00:04:36.920 --> 00:04:39.958
kh'ken nor tsugebn, fun tsayt tsu tsayt,

00:04:40.170 --> 00:04:41.358
di froy

00:04:41.650 --> 00:04:43.771
bakumt a bisl shtitse

00:04:44.013 --> 00:04:45.530
fun JOINT,

00:04:45.802 --> 00:04:47.838
un dos helft tsu

00:04:48.266 --> 00:04:52.378
tsum materyeln lebn

00:04:52.910 --> 00:04:54.360
in der familye.

00:04:56.535 --> 00:04:58.140
ah hot ir

00:04:58.140 --> 00:05:00.910
fotos fun di familye, oder

00:05:01.057 --> 00:05:03.223
ir, fotos fun dem

00:05:03.167 --> 00:05:05.929
ikh hob, nor ikh hob nisht bay zikh do,

00:05:03.223 --> 00:05:04.865
fun der milkhome.

00:05:06.103 --> 00:05:07.228
a shod.

00:05:08.111 --> 00:05:11.582
ven ikh volt gevust genoy az me darf hobn di fotos,

00:05:12.080 --> 00:05:14.349
ikh ken tsugebn di fotos.

00:05:14.730 --> 00:05:16.520
ikh ken nor efsher

00:05:16.780 --> 00:05:18.753
bald, epes, oy!

00:05:19.760 --> 00:05:23.930
ikh perzenlekh mitn Vrotslaver muzeum,

00:05:24.783 --> 00:05:26.300
greytn mir tsu

00:05:26.300 --> 00:05:27.731
in Vrotslav

00:05:28.243 --> 00:05:30.580
a groyse oysshtelung,

00:05:30.860 --> 00:05:33.170
foto-oysshtelung,

00:05:33.730 --> 00:05:36.618
fun dem gevezenem yidishn yishev

00:05:36.663 --> 00:05:38.260
in Nidershlezyen.

