oyf dem gebit,

00:06:35.928 --> 00:06:38.360
oyb ir vilt kent ir araynnemen

00:06:38.560 --> 00:06:40.816
dem briv in dem film,

00:06:41.730 --> 00:06:44.840
vos ikh hob genoy ibergegebn

00:06:46.644 --> 00:06:48.377
in muzeum arayn,

00:06:48.770 --> 00:06:52.224
tsu organizirn di oysshtelung.

00:06:55.183 --> 00:06:56.814
oyb dos iz vikhtik

00:06:58.355 --> 00:07:00.966
kent ir es onnemen

00:06:58.524 --> 00:06:59.273
yo.

