mayn film-bashraybung.

00:07:08.430 --> 00:07:11.040
ir kent es fotografirn oyb ir vilt.

00:07:17.250 --> 00:07:19.340
far der tsukunft,

00:07:20.450 --> 00:07:22.450
farn yidishn yishev,

