mit undzer yidisher shprakh, mit undzer yidisher kultur un literatur,

00:07:33.740 --> 00:07:37.140
iz vi lor- vi nor s'iz meglekh

00:07:37.830 --> 00:07:40.380
farshpreytn dos yidishe vort,

00:07:41.300 --> 00:07:43.280
dos yidishe kunst,

00:07:43.960 --> 00:07:47.653
dos vos alts hot a shaykhes mit der yidisher kultur,

00:07:47.653 --> 00:07:49.296
mit der yidisher literatur,

00:07:49.503 --> 00:07:51.286
in der yidisher shprakh.

00:07:51.579 --> 00:07:52.788
di shprakh

00:07:53.030 --> 00:07:55.033
zol nisht untergeyn

00:07:55.160 --> 00:07:57.463
vi lang se lebt nokh in Poyln

00:07:57.570 --> 00:07:59.170
a yidisher yishev.

00:08:02.683 --> 00:08:04.250
vos ken men nokh

00:08:04.370 --> 00:08:06.170
tsugebn tsu dem?

00:08:07.300 --> 00:08:08.620
leyder,

00:08:08.977 --> 00:08:11.182
di yidishe institutsyes

00:08:11.340 --> 00:08:12.684
in Poyln

00:08:13.650 --> 00:08:15.080
geyen avek

00:08:15.360 --> 00:08:17.330
fun der yidisher shprakh.

00:08:17.520 --> 00:08:20.002
alts in der arbet

00:08:20.002 --> 00:08:22.100
kumt for in der poylisher shprakh.

00:08:22.983 --> 00:08:24.361
ikh farshtey,

00:08:25.760 --> 00:08:26.859
dos iz

00:08:27.067 --> 00:08:28.496
in a tsayt

