00:08:31.410 --> 00:08:32.934
di virklekhkeyt

00:08:33.328 --> 00:08:34.571
iz aza,

00:08:35.623 --> 00:08:37.845
vos s'iz ummeglekh

00:08:38.407 --> 00:08:41.405
tog-teglekh tsu banitsn di yidishe shprakh.

00:08:41.495 --> 00:08:42.440
derfar,

00:08:42.440 --> 00:08:43.930
se feln shoyn

00:08:43.930 --> 00:08:45.236
di mentshn,

00:08:45.530 --> 00:08:46.665
der dor,

00:08:46.665 --> 00:08:48.965
velkher hot geredt in der yidisher shprakh.

00:08:56.126 --> 00:08:57.820
dos bin ikh,

00:08:58.438 --> 00:09:00.424
Robak Henrik,

